{"tid":506867,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【YouTube戒賭新招】賭博數學入門？","createTime":"2017-12-22T15:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T15:49:17.000Z","uid":123228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d476c9933d7545c145429d165761f9eb8f02bec9","tid":506867,"uid":123228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的，又係我杜氏數學Herman To，話說我已經拍攝好一系列5堂嘅《賭博數學入門》短片，暫時發佈咗第一堂：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QLE4keUg1Qo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQLE4keUg1Qo&d=4MxJQVgQqs6CX8oCnslF2MmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=cf5ffbbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QLE4keUg1Qo</a><br />\n<br />\n介紹返，我嘅理念係：只要徹底明白賭博背後嘅數學原理，知道（而唔單只係相信）常賭必輸，自然就唔會豪賭咁蠢。<br />\n<br />\n接觸過唔少「賭大、賭細、賭埋一家大細」嘅賭徒，賭到又拜神、又戴呢樣、戴嗰樣、著曬紅底褲之類，其實呢啲悲劇都係源自對賭博嘅陌生&mdash;&mdash;當人類唔認識一樣嘢嘅時候，就會幻想好多方法去理解佢，甚至會賴個老婆剋夫，或者仔女陀衰家。<br />\n<br />\n作為識些少數學嘅人，除咗講DSE數學考試之外，我都希望可以講解多啲賭博數學，但求做到：當賭輸嘅時候，知道輸啲乜，唔好再有咁多迷信嘢，越踩越深。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴打絲打都支持下，如果認識沉迷賭博嘅親朋戚友，歡迎你轉載畀佢地睇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/233815_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F233815_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=05758ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n*PDF講義連習題可以去我官網下載"},{"pid":"3c0cc8793eaa987e53b03fc7c74dad5a993f111a","tid":506867,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:43:17.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"5b5cbd4812f26f985b0f2463f7c65e9cb965c8f9","tid":506867,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"把聲唔似呢個身材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}